  "id": 3,
  "title": {
    "zh": "週末做什麼？",
    "pinyin": "Zhōumò zuò shénme?",
    "de": "What do you do on the weekend?"
  },
  "objectives": [
    "Describe leisure activities",
    "Make invitations with 吧",
    "Form suggestions with 怎麼樣 / 好不好",
    "Use 也, 都, and 常 correctly"
